 SECTION ANALYSIS AND RATINGS

 - [**GENERAL STRUCTURE**] Rating: 4/5
   Solid Next.js/Express foundation.

 - [**CODE QUALITY**] Rating: 3.5/5
   Clean structure, but lacks tests and has some dead code (`validation.js`).

 - [**SECURITY**] Rating: 4/5
   Drastically improved by removing auth. Weak XSS protection is the only remaining note.

 - [**CONTENT & FUNCTIONALITY**] Rating: 4/5
   Core news reading features are present and working. Search is basic.

 - [**PERFORMANCE & OPTIMIZATION**] Rating: 4/5
   Caching and pagination are huge wins. Search needs optimization.

 - [**SEO & SOCIAL META**] Rating: 4.5/5
   Strong SEO implementation with JSON-LD and dynamic meta tags.

 - [**DEPLOYMENT & DEVOPS**] Rating: 4/5
   CI/CD and Vercel config are good.
